    "name": "Roger Subirana",
    "profile": "Compositor and musical producer born in Vilafranca del Penedès (Barcelona). Proud of his land, he has created several works that recall the flavors and smells of the vineyard and cava. As a child he set a trend and his first compositions were carried out before he was 12 years old.\r\n\r\nIn his extensive discography we find the most personal music, built as an experiential diary expressing an infinite range of feelings experienced in different stages of his life. For this reason it is so difficult to pigeonhole it in a specific musical style. Eclectic and serene in equal parts. It does not hide anything behind the notes. His pieces are small soundtracks, where in some songs the voice is used as a pure instrument, hence the lyrics are phonetic and have no semantic interpretation. Look for the musicality of the voice without being tied to the dictionary, thus achieving a creation in its pure state. He defines himself as \"Composer of Instrumental and Phonics Music\".\r\n\r\nApart from his discogr",
